## Input

```css
@each $item in $list {
  color: $item;
}

@each $key, $value in $map {
  color: $key;
  background: $value;
}

@each $animal in puma, sea-slug, egret, salamander {
  color: red;
}

@each $name, $size in (
  h1: 32px,
  h2: 24px,
) {
  font-size: $size;
}

@each $tuple in (puma, black), (egret, white) {
  color: red;
}

```


